  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Circular 004/2020: Firearms licensing - EU exit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This circular sets out changes to firearms legislation as a result of the UK's exit from the EU.</p>

  </div>
</div>

